-X POST
-d @filename.json (json in request body)
-e 'http://...' referer
-H 'Accept: text/html,...' header -H can be repeated
-u 'username:password' (for basic auth)
-d 'form_key=value1&anotherkey=value2&.....' POST PARAMS
-i get response headers
--trace filename To check that all headers/params are ok
-A '...' Sets the user agent
